0721.name: Unknown
0721.message:
Online Interaction is restricted by
Parental Controls
0721.long_description: Your parental controls settings has disallowed your console from going online.
0721.short_solution:
Reset your parental controls or visit here:
https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/270/~/how-to-reset-parental-controls
0721.long_solution: Enable online in your parental controls. See Nintendo's official support pages https://www.nintendo.com.au/support/articles/001-0721 and https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/270/~/how-to-reset-parental-controls
